OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,FCorrespondent Charlotte Cross speaks
OL,7,Fto police and the council leader to
OL,8,Ffind out what they're doing to tackle
OL,9,Fthe biggest issues facing residents in
OL,10,FRedditch
OL,12,FIt's a popular commuter town
OL,13,Fsurrounded by the glorious
OL,14,FWorcestershire countryside and
OL,15,Fboasting beautiful parks like Arrow
OL,16,FValley.
OL,18,FBut Redditch also struggles with
OL,19,Fpoverty - with more than half of
OL,20,Fhouseholds classed as 'deprived' in at
OL,21,Fleast one category.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
