OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,FSo who better to ask about what needs
OL,7,Fto change than the people who live
OL,8,Fthere?
OL,10,FI spent a day in the town centre
OL,11,Fspeaking to Redditch residents about
OL,12,Fjust that - and there were some common
OL,13,Fthemes which came up in conversation.
OL,15,FThe number of empty shops situated
OL,16,Foutside the Kingfisher Shopping Centre
OL,17,Fwas a key point of concern - and so
OL,18,Fwas the amount of drug use.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
