OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,F"I'm not sure why it's happening, but
OL,7,Fit just lets the tone down really,"
OL,8,Fone person told me.
OL,10,F"And the more people that use drugs,
OL,11,Fthe more people become desperate. More
OL,12,Fpeople need money. Then that's when
OL,13,Fthings like crime increases."
OL,15,FSo how big is the problem?
OL,17,FTo try to get to the bottom of it, I
OL,18,Fasked West Mercia Police how many drug-
OL,19,Frelated crimes were recorded in
OL,20,FRedditch between January last year and
OL,21,FJune this year.
