OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,FFigures revealed a total of 299
OL,7,Foffences recorded in the borough
OL,8,Facross that period - and it is
OL,9,Fsignificantly higher than neighbouring
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,FThis is 15% higher than in Wychavon,
OL,13,Fwhich had 261 offences in that time;
OL,14,Fand 39% more than Bromsgrove which had
OL,15,Fa total of 215 recorded offences.
OL,17,FPC Mike Moore who looks after the town
OL,18,Fcentre said drug and alcohol misuse is
OL,19,Ftheir "biggest policing priority".
OL,26,@{D@GOU{D@aO]
