OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,F"Drug and alcohol misuse leads to
OL,7,Fthefts. The desperation of some of
OL,8,Fthese individuals can lead to disorder
OL,9,Famongst themselves more than anybody
OL,10,Felse," he said.
