OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,F"We do tackle the drug issues in
OL,7,FRedditch quite robustly. About 12 to
OL,8,F18 months ago, we had the Public Space
OL,9,FProtection Order put in place in
OL,10,FRedditch. And that was authorised by
OL,11,Fthe local authority. So that gives us
OL,12,Fextra powers in the town. If there's
OL,13,Fany antisocial behaviour within the
OL,14,Farea where it's geographically
OL,15,Frelated, we can disperse individuals
OL,16,Fup to 48 hours, and if you continue
OL,17,Fbreaching that order, can lead to an
OL,18,Fappearance in court.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
