OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1759503558
OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,F"But we've got to look at the long
OL,7,Fterm. Intervention as such is where
OL,8,Fwe're not solely looking at
OL,9,Fprosecuting these individuals, some of
OL,10,Fthese individuals have had big traumas
OL,11,Fin their life, which has led to
OL,12,Falcohol and substance misuse. So we
OL,13,Fbrought in the MAGS charity from
OL,14,FWorcester.
OL,16,F"And what we do there, home reduction
OL,17,Fworkers will come out with us and
OL,18,Fspeak to individuals - see if there
OL,19,Fare any needs which they require, such
OL,20,Fas a doctor's appointments, dentist
OL,21,Fappointments, and so on.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
