OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,F"But dealing with the long term is to
OL,7,Fprevent that continually happening. We
OL,8,Fcan keep prosecuting people, sending
OL,9,Fthem to the courts, and if we do go to
OL,10,Fprison, putting orders on them, but
OL,11,Fthen they're released from prison and
OL,12,Fthey're back doing the same thing
OL,13,Fagain. And this has been going on for
OL,14,Fdecades. So I think we need to look
OL,15,Foutside the box."
OL,17,FAnd he said the approach is starting
OL,18,Fto yield results.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@QO]
