OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,F"Myself in particular and other
OL,7,Fofficers, I've got a really good
OL,8,Frapport with a lot of the individuals,
OL,9,Fwhich we didn't necessarily have
OL,10,Fprobably 18 months ago. They are
OL,11,Fturning up to appointments. Their
OL,12,Fcriminal activity has dropped
OL,13,Fsignificantly," he said.
OL,15,F"We understand there will be blips in
OL,16,Ftheir behaviour. It ain't gonna happen
OL,17,Fovernight. You know, it's going to
OL,18,Ftake time to deal with this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@OO]wD@AOU
