OL,3,CEmpty shops, poor transport and a drug
OL,4,Cproblem: What can be done for Redditch?
OL,6,FTo try to get those answers, I met
OL,7,Fwith the leader of Redditch Borough
OL,8,FCouncil, Cllr Sharon Harvey, to ask
OL,9,Fwhat she and her cabinet are doing.
OL,11,FTo see what she had to say, watch the
OL,12,Ffull episode of 'What's the Big Deal
OL,13,Fin Redditch?' here, and over on ITVX.
OL,15,FAnd don't worry - it's not all doom
OL,16,Fand gloom. I also asked people what
OL,17,Fthey loved about Redditch - with Arrow
OL,18,FValley park a popular highlight, along
OL,19,Fwith the theatre, its key location,
OL,20,Fand the shopping centre itself.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
